<3>Bitwise operator

Choose the correct output of the following code:
public static void main (String[] args) {
    int a=10,b=20;
    int c=a&b;
    System.out.print(c);
    int d=a|b;
    System.out.print(d);
    int e=a^b;
    System.out.print(e);
    int f=c+d+e;
    System.out.print(~f);
}
Options
03030-60
03030-61 
0303060
03030-59

Correct Answer
03030-61
Solution Description
c=10&20=0.
d=10|20=30. 
e=10^20=30.
f=0+30+30=60.
 ~f=-61.

