<7> Guess the output

class Solution {
    public static void main(String args[]) 
    {   
    int x = 15;
    int y = x++;
    int  z = ++x;
    System.out.println(y +" " + z);
    }
}
Options
15 16
16 17
15 17 
16 16

Correct Answer
15 17
Solution Description
x = 15
post increment y 
y = 15
then x value increments by 1, x = 16
z is pre increment: x = 17
z = 17

