<8> Guess the output

class Solution {
    public static void main(String args[]) 
    {        
         int g = 3;
         System.out.print(++g * 8);
    } 
}
Options
24
32 
Correct Answer
32
Solution Description
print: g + 1 * 8 = 4 * 8 = 32

