<11> Select the correct output for the following code:

public static void main (String[] args) {
    int a=5;
    a+=5+(++a)+(a++);
    System.out.print(a);
} 
Options
20
22 
17
18

Correct Answer
22
Solution Description
a=a+5+(++a)+(a++).  
=5+5+6+6=22


