<12> Guess the Output

public static void main (String] args) {
    int a=10;
    a+=++a-5/3+6*a;
    System.out.print(a);
}
Options
50
70
76
86 
Correct Answer
86
Solution Description
a+=++a-5/3+6*a.
a+=11-1+6*11.
a=10+11-1+66=86.


